This is a sample of an app that shows a nap of the Student repeate rate in Secondary education for Colombia

Figures in %

Notes of this map This map was draws data from ESRI open data Colombia

Features

  • The map depicts just one variable but more variables and layers can be added

  • The application is ‘live’ in the same way that spreadsheets are live. Outputs change instantly as users modify inputs, without requiring a reload of the browser.

  • We can adapt the layers, colours, labels and more if required
